Jean-Louis Weissberg. « La crise fiduciaire des medias de masse. Je crois parce que j’experimente. »  Multitudes 21, http://multitudes.samizdat.net/article.php3?id_article=1978. 

I particularly recommend the above essay, an extended meditation on the crisis of trust affecting institutional media, and the epistemological characteristics of the new situation.

It's part of a special issue of the French journal Multitudes on the topic of subjectivation in the postmedia age, at http://multitudes.samizdat.net/rubrique.php3?id_rubrique=612